===Other entrants===
The following players received wildcards into the singles main draw:
* {{flagicon|ITA}} [[Fabio Fognini]]
* {{flagicon|DEN}} [[Frederik Nielsen]]
* {{flagicon|CZE}} [[Luk<U+00E1><U+0161> Rosol]]
* {{flagicon|ITA}} [[Andreas Seppi]]

The following players received entry from the qualifying draw:
* {{flagicon|GER}} [[Andre Begemann]]
* {{flagicon|ITA}} [[Alberto Brizzi]]
* {{flagicon|ITA}} [[Marco Crugnola]]
* {{flagicon|ARG}} [[Renzo Olivo]]

